As a consultant the role includes:

column2: Assistance in budget determination and breakdown as needed
Discussion of theme, colour, style and complete wedding design
Research of wedding professionals in each category that fit your event style and budget and to provide you with suggestions and guidance in making the final selections
Transfers organization for the wedding day (if needed)
Attendance at vendor appointments of your choice depending on travel expenses
Professional in-person consultation time throughout the planning process
Development of a detailed wedding timeline and floor plan for contracted vendors and bridal party
Follow up telephone calls to all contracted vendors 1 – 2 weeks before wedding day

column1: As Wedding Day Coordinator my duties include:

column2: Walk through at the venue for a complete recap of the ceremony and reception on previous days
Day-Of Coordination with no time limitation
